1
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:23,870
Now that you’ve met Ranya,

2
00:00:23,890 --> 00:00:25,430
what do you think, Mr. Kim?

3
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:27,770
She’s beautiful.

4
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:31,820
I think we’ll get along quite well.

5
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:37,650
Ranya is a very good girl.

6
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:40,410
She’s polite, well-mannered, and sweet.

7
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,290
That’s great to hear.

8
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,880
Um, excuse me...

9
00:00:47,550 --> 00:00:49,770
what are you talking about?

10
00:00:52,820 --> 00:00:55,400
This is Mr. Kimhant,

11
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:57,500
the Chairman of Holder Group.

12
00:00:58,310 --> 00:01:00,400
I want you two to get to know each other

13
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,880
since you’re going to be getting engaged, after all.

14
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:04,180
Wait...

15
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,230
what?!

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,120
It’s a pleasure to meet you, Khun Ranya.

17
00:01:23,821 --> 00:01:24,744
Excuse me, I have to leave now.

18
00:01:30,024 --> 00:01:33,716
Oh, um... Ranya is probably just feeling shy.

19
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:35,409
I’m so sorry about that.

20
00:01:35,433 --> 00:01:38,129
Let me go bring her back.

21
00:01:38,153 --> 00:01:39,230
It’s quite alright.

22
00:01:42,210 --> 00:01:44,960
I actually like this,

23
00:01:45,298 --> 00:01:46,196
she’s a challenge.

24
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,230
Hey, Ranya!

25
00:02:07,563 --> 00:02:08,098
Ranya!

26
00:02:08,603 --> 00:02:10,055
How could you just walk out like that?!

27
00:02:10,050 --> 00:02:11,341
It’s incredibly rude.

28
00:02:11,692 --> 00:02:13,267
Get back in there and talk to Mr. Kimhant right now!

29
00:02:14,609 --> 00:02:16,600
Mom, why are you trying to force me to talk to him?

30
00:02:17,692 --> 00:02:19,690
And what’s with this ridiculous engagement nonsense?

31
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:23,070
I’m doing this for your own good!

32
00:02:23,390 --> 00:02:26,043
Mr. Kimhant is the one who can help you become the President.

33
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,883
Mom!

34
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:31,341
Having a good backing is half the battle won.

35
00:02:31,770 --> 00:02:34,295
Right now, you’re at a disadvantage compared to Pimchat.

36
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,193
Listen to me, Mom.

37
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:42,738
From now on, I’m not doing what you tell me anymore.

38
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,670
And that goes for this crazy engagement business, too.

39
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:51,489
I already have someone I love.

40
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:01,624
Love?

41
00:03:02,770 --> 00:03:05,132
Do you dare to call it "love"?

42
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:08,412
What do you mean?

43
00:03:13,563 --> 00:03:15,520
If you don’t do as I say,

44
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:20,701
I’ll release the evidence that you’re seeing Pimchat,

45
00:03:21,507 --> 00:03:23,212
your own half-sister.

46
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,618
Look at this...

47
00:03:38,264 --> 00:03:40,260
I have the video right here on my phone.

48
00:03:59,950 --> 00:04:00,560
Mom...

49
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:04,270
why would you do this to me?

50
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,384
Like I told you, dear,

51
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,836
I only want what's best for you.

52
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:19,396
Just marry Mr. Kimhant,

53
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:22,264
and everything will be fine.

54
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,790
And if I refuse?

55
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:35,729
Then I might accidentally leave this phone in a restroom somewhere at the company.

56
00:04:40,701 --> 00:04:43,624
Let go dear, Mr. Kim has been waiting for a long time.

57
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,664
No.

58
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:29,076
But it’s the best way, P'Chat.

59
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,753
No, Ran.

60
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:36,800
But if everyone finds out we aren’t actually sibling

61
00:05:38,086 --> 00:05:40,080
you’ll get your legal rights back.

62
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,836
Then you’ll finally be able to deal with Mom.

63
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:45,815
But if we do that, you’ll get into trouble, too.

64
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:48,590
Absolutely.

65
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,630
I am her daughter.

66
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,175
I think I have a better plan.

67
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,116
How?

68
00:06:02,904 --> 00:06:07,323
Right now, Jintana thinks she has the majority of the board members on her side.

69
00:06:08,529 --> 00:06:11,341
She’s bound to abuse her power.

70
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:16,049
I’m planning to use that against her.

71
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,526
But everyone is going to find out eventually anyway.

72
00:06:20,490 --> 00:06:22,978
They’ll find out after we expose what she did wrong.

73
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:27,169
And then I’ll tell everyone that you’ve been on my side all along.

74
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:30,929
Trust me, okay?

75
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:32,695
I do.

76
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:36,018
I’ll help you however I can, P’Chat.

77
00:06:37,250 --> 00:06:41,169
Besides, Mom doesn't suspect a thing about me yet.

78
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,018
Don’t be sulky with me.

79
00:07:09,770 --> 00:07:10,769
I’m not sulky.

80
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:16,147
I’m mad.

81
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:27,378
I just thought it was the only way to make Mom let her guard down

82
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,544
and feel like she has me under her thumb.

83
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:35,655
Who knows? She might even be secretly conspiring with Mr. Kimhant.

84
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,003
It’ll be fine, P’Chat.

85
00:07:43,735 --> 00:07:45,470
I can take care of myself.

86
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:46,880
Don’t worry.

87
00:07:47,938 --> 00:07:50,055
I know you can take care of yourself.

88
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,947
But I’m possessive.

89
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,812
I thought you said you were mad?

90
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:13,796
I am, but my possessiveness is stronger.

91
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:17,741
Who would actually like this?

92
00:08:17,766 --> 00:08:19,643
Letting their own girlfriend become someone else’s fiancée.

93
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,467
Stop being so cute.

94
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:51,360
Is that all?

95
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,806
You want more?

96
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,710
I won't be playing nice then.

97
00:09:00,330 --> 00:09:01,987
Fine... I’ll let you have your way for one day.
